rows.label: tlk42400013_06_msg0001
rows.name:
Due to the collapse of
Acedia, everyone everywhere
is extremely busy, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_06_msg0002
rows.name:
We're dispatching help
from Avaritia to assist
with accepting refugees.

rows.label: tlk42400013_06_msg0003
rows.name:
We're also arranging for the
necessary supplies, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_06_msg0004
rows.name:
Helping each other is
important in this world, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_06_msg0005
rows.name:
If you see someone in trouble, be
proactive in helping them, mo.
